description:
Epilog Laser, the leading producer of CO2 and fiber laser engraving, cutting, and marking systems, is excited to announce the introduction of the new Fusion Maker to the company‚Äôs product line. This highly-anticipated machine incorporates some of the most popular features of Epilog‚Äôs Fusion Pro and Edge Series in a small-format affordable 3D laser printer.

Epilog Fusion Maker Laser Machine
https://www.epiloglaser.com/laser-machines/fusion-maker-laser-cutter-engraver/

Featuring a 24‚Äù x 12‚Äù x 7‚Äù (610 x 305 x 178 mm) work area, the Fusion Maker is available in 30 or 40 CO2 laser source configurations. It also includes Epilog‚Äôs IRIS‚Ñ¢ Camera Positioning System, which gives operators a live-view image of the laser bed to precisely position their artwork and graphics quickly and accurately.

The IRIS‚Ñ¢ Camera System is, hands down, the fastest and easiest camera positioning system available,‚Äù said Mike Dean, vice president of sales and marketing for Epilog Laser. ‚ÄúIt‚Äôs an incredibly valuable tool for our customers, and we‚Äôre excited to offer this new technology in a compact system.

Additional features of the Fusion Edge include:
- 24" x 12" (610 x 305 mm) engraving area
- 30 or 40-watt CO2 Laser
- 7" (178 mm) z-depth

In line with all of Epilog‚Äôs product offerings, the Fusion Maker features the highest-quality components for durability and low lifetime ownership costs and is proudly designed, engineered, and manufactured in the USA.

title: Beparwah (Official Video) | Sidhant Kapoor X Ruskin Bond X The Sunshine Orchestra
description:
Sidhant Kapoor, a music composer, was so moved by a poetry called ‚ÄòSlum Children at Play‚Äô by Ruskin Bond, that he drove up the hills of Mussoorie to meet the legendary writer and seek permission to put his words to music. On returning to Mumbai, Sidhant took notice of three street children and realised that they personify the emotions of the poetry. With this inspiration, Sidhant began his journey of composing his first ever single! He brought The Sunshine Orchestra, legendary composer A.R. Rahman's dream project, on board to perform the strings section. He wrote additional lyrics in Hindi and started painting the first few strokes of this composition. All through this process, he was inspired by the story of the three kids that taught him the true meaning of ‚ÄòBeparwah‚Äô!

No angels these,

Because that‚Äôs what you are ‚Äì
You‚Äôre just a joke ‚Äì

title: Lead Generation for Private Jet Industry & Understanding Customer Qualification
description:
Private/charter jets industry is a niche market that caters to a high-end clientele seeking luxury travel experiences. Understanding this industry can help in lead generation and customer qualification. Here are some key aspects to consider:

1. Target market: Private/charter jets are primarily used by high-net-worth individuals, corporate executives, celebrities, and government officials. Therefore, understanding the demographics and psychographics of this target market can help in lead generation and customer qualification.

2. Services and amenities: Private/charter jets offer a range of services and amenities such as personalized in-flight catering, luxury interiors, and advanced entertainment systems. Understanding the specific needs and preferences of the target market can help in tailoring the services and amenities to attract and retain customers.

3. Price and value: Private/charter jets are expensive, and pricing varies based on the type of aircraft, distance, and duration of the flight. Understanding the value proposition of the service and communicating it effectively to potential customers can help in generating leads and qualifying customers.

4. Reputation and referrals: Reputation and referrals play a crucial role in the private/charter jets industry. Positive reviews and referrals from satisfied customers can help in generating new leads and qualifying potential customers.

5. Industry regulations: The private/charter jets industry is highly regulated, and compliance with regulations is critical for lead generation and customer qualification. Understanding and complying with industry regulations can help build trust and credibility with potential customers.

6. Compliance: The private/charter jets industry is highly regulated, and it's important to comply with regulations when advertising on Facebook and Google. Be transparent about pricing, disclose any fees or surcharges, and avoid making misleading claims.

title: Focus Episode 1 + Addition Ad Desktop Arrow CTA
Staying On Brand With Grammarly Business
The benefits of writing by hand | Katie McCleary | TEDxEustis
description: Leadership professor and writing and consciousness expert, Katie McCleary, MFA, offers the benefits of writing by hand for all ages. Based on more than 25 years of writing with thousands of people, McCleary offers insights into the science of handwriting and how it can easily improve your focus, elevate your thinking, deliver the ‚Äústicky factor‚Äù to retain new learning, and create more meaningful, resonate connections. So, go ahead, let go of the grammar police, write in your messy unique font, and see what bubbles up when you try slow and write by hand. Katie McCleary is an author, changemaker, professor of leadership and a lover of people. Earning her MFA, in Writing and Consciousness, led to her belief that handwriting is a path to transform the self, communities and the world. She is also the coauthor of Bridge the Gap, which Inc. named 1 of 3 business books to read in 2022. As the founder of the nonprofit, 916 Ink, Katie has helped more than 4500 young people become confident authors who know the power of the pen. Mashable.com named her 1 of 15 ‚ÄúReal Miss Americas‚Äù for her career in uplifting communities. She is the host of NPR CapRadio‚Äôs leadership podcast, ‚ÄúThe Drive.‚Äù Katie teaches in the Masters of Nonprofit Leadership at Pacific University. Her work has appeared in Forbes, PBS, Shondaland, Thrive, Apple News, and Hip Mama. She lives with 2 children, 15 chickens, 1 talkative parrot, and other furry creatures in California. She is handwriting her next book: A Biomythography of Our Being: What We Become when We Write. This talk was given at a TEDx event using the TED conference format but independently organized by a local community. Learn more at https://www.ted.com/tedx

Playback Records Presents Sufi Vibes.

A show designed to bring out the best of the talent based in Dubai. 

A AAA Reels Production and Playback Creatives Presentation, this show is a celebration of the rich cultural heritage and spiritual essence of Sufism, with a lineup of soul-stirring songs that will transport you to a world of divine love and mystical bliss.

A Sufi song that is a heartfelt ode to the Divine. The repetitive chanting of " Ishq na kar bethi‚Äù creates a meditative and hypnotic effect that transports the listener to a state of trance. The song can be interpreted in different ways depending on the context. For some, it may convey a sense of helplessness and vulnerability in the face of love's overwhelming power. For others, it may be a celebration of the courage and passion required to pursue love despite the risks involved.

description:
#ExtemporeMusicalJourney #podcast #guitarist 

‚ñ∫Podcast With Paras Ft.Vinod Katoch (Full Episode)

Welcome to Extempore Musical Journeys! I'm excited to introduce you to this unique and exciting project created in collaboration with Two for Joy Studio. Extempore Musical Journeys takes you on a musical voyage like no other, where the destination and musical style are unknown, and the journey is completely improvised. Each episode features talented musicians who come together to create something truly special in the moment. This project is all about pushing boundaries and exploring the unknown, and we can't wait for you to come along for the ride. Get ready for an unforgettable musical experience that will leave you wanting more.
A Pantellisense Production!

‚ñ∫Podcast With Paras Ft.Vinod Katoch (Full Episode)

Episode 3 of Extempore Musical Journeys with Paras and Vinod takes us on a journey to discover finger style guitar. Paras starts off by explaining the basics of finger style guitar and demonstrates a few techniques.

Vinod then picks up his guitar and they start playing Mohit Chauhan's popular song 'Boondein' in finger style. The music is soothing and mesmerizing as their fingers move effortlessly on the strings, producing beautiful melodies.

As they continue playing, Paras and Vinod share their experiences with finger style guitar and how it has opened up new musical avenues for them. They also discuss the importance of practice and perseverance in mastering the technique.

The episode ends with a soulful rendition of 'Boondein' in finger style, leaving the viewers mesmerized and wanting more of such melodious and informative musical journeys.

description:
Desi Melodies presents in association with Cape Of Good Films & Azeem Dayani the first single, 'Kya Loge Tum,' from B Praak's highly anticipated debut album, "Zohrajabeen." The star-studded team of B Praak, Jaani, Arvindr Khaira, and Akshay Kumar reunites for the first time since the pop-culture-defining songs 'Filhall' and 'Filhaal 2.'

The emotionally charged lyrics written by Jaani, along with his heart-wrenching composition, add an extra layer of depth to the already powerful track produced by B Praak himself. title: Tin Hearts | The Little Soldier Who Dared - Narrated By Stephen Fry
description:
Discover more about Tin Hearts: https://wiredproductions.com/games/tin-hearts/
Find where to buy: https://wiredproductions.com/games/tin-hearts/#where-to-buy

Narrated by Stephen Fry, The Little Soldier Who Dared is a prequel to the video game Tin Hearts. Albert, an inventor of Victorian times, and his daughter Rose travel to a toymaking convention to show off their wares and have an important meeting, the outcome of which could forever change their destiny. Albert's toys however are special in ways unknown even to him! What goes on at night when the convention hall is emptied of its crowds? And if Albert gets his wish, will it be quite what he was expecting? 

The Little Soldier Who Dared is narrated by legend Stephen Fry, written by Kostas Zarifis and Mike Faraday, Art by Taufiq Permana, Animation by Thor Hayton and Sound & Music by Matthew Chastney.

In Tin Hearts, guide a troop of mischievous tin soldiers through a magical toy-filled world using a variety of whimsical and inventive contraptions to bounce, shoot and glide them to their goal. March through 40+ levels of time-bending, soldier-routing riddles, forge new paths for your toys to follow, and solve increasingly elaborate puzzles to unravel the emotional, thought-provoking story, of Albert J. Butterworth, a genius inventor of Victorian times.

Tin Hearts was released on Nintendo Switch on April 20th, 2023 with PC (Steam, Epic Games Store, GOG, Utomik), PlayStation 4 & 5, and the Xbox family of consoles to release one month later on May 16th, 2023. PCVR, Meta Quest 2 and PSVR2 are set to be released later this year.

title: VERIVERY - 'Crazy Like That' Official M/V
description:
VERIVERY ‚Äì A Trendy Icon Acknowledged by All
With the release of [Liminality ‚Äì EP.LOVE] last November, VERIVERY had managed to sweep multiple awards from ceremonies on top of achieving first place on music programs.

And in May 2023, VERIVERY returns with their second story through [Liminality ‚Äì EP.DREAM].
 
DREAM: The Second Element of Happiness
In [Liminality ‚Äì EP.LOVE], VERIVERY had expressed the emotion of ‚Äòlove‚Äô through a number of different ways. This time, through [Liminality ‚Äì EP.DREAM], VERIVERY shows off their intuitive, unique colors in the process of achieving their DREAM.

To PLAY in the Present, or PLAN for the Future
VERIVERY plans to show two different paths towards their DREAM.
With the ‚ÄòPLAY‚Äô version emphasizing one‚Äôs happiness in the moment, and ‚ÄòPLAN‚Äô version focusing on meticulously preparing for their future, the members will appeal to all through two contrasting sides.
The jacket expresses the journey towards a DREAM through both a ‚ÄòPLAY‚Äô-focused path, bringing energy to a chaotic yet humble space, and a ‚ÄòPLAN‚Äô-focused path, where building a blueprint for the future is portrayed in a mature, intellectual way. 
As well, the music video shows the members striving towards their DREAM in both unrestrained strides and steady, passionate steps to show the qualities unique to each of the two paths. As each of their individual spaces come together to create a common area, the members also come together in making the achievement of their DREAM a common goal.

Liminality - EP. DREAM, the Expansion of VERIVERY
Through the [Liminality - EP.DREAM] album, VERIVERY brings to light their ever-expanding musical spectrum. Through new styles of music, performance, and visuals, the group promises to show off yet another distinct, artistic side to them.
VERIVERY welcomes all into their space filled with their DREAM, so that we could all step into and explore their ‚ÄòDREAM‚Äô home using their unique key.
